                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120219-35-off209 t18120219-35-crimeloc212"></join>, I am a waiter in his employ. On the 23d of January the prisoner came into the coffee-room, and ordered tea; he paid for his tea, he ran away with the spoon and the sugar-tongs; I had seen the tea-spoon about two minutes before he left the room. I pursued him, and took him with the spoon and tongs upon him, these are the things, they are my master's property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am truly sorry.</p>
